<paragraph id="2F54B5B36459DB585FBF85C1532A50C8" pageId="66" pageNumber="91">Thailand: Lamphun, Nakhon Phanom, Kanchanaburi, Bangkok, Ranong, Phangnga, Krabi, Trang, Songkhla, Yala. Tropics.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
